name: cats fighting giant squid
description:
"cats fighting giant squid" from the critically acclaimed series Cats Fighting Stuff. This is the first cats fighting stuff mint of '22. 

From Squid Digest Monthly, "cats fighting giant squid is a triumphant homage to a future world where cats battle giant squid on both land and sea. No doubt this work presents a sober assessment of an inevitable future."

From the New York Times,"In the grand scheme of things it's probably worth 1 tez. Maybe even 1.5."

This is part V of Cat's Fighting Stuff.
